            "The Father of \u2018Two Bombs\u2019",
            "Deng Jiaxian always stood at the forefront of China\u2019s atomic weapons design and research, leading many scholars and technicians to successfully design China\u2019s atomic and hydrogen bombs.",
            "\u2018To give one\u2019s all until death\u2019 describes his life precisely.",
            "Eternal Pride",
