            "\u2018If he says it\u2019s not fresh, he must have his reasons. It\u2019s wrong to dismiss his judgment without checking.\u2019",
            "Mr. Lu Xun knew his health was failing and he didn\u2019t have many years of work left. Dying didn\u2019t matter\u2014what mattered was leaving more for humanity."
