            "At first, Sun Quan said to L\u00fc Meng: \u2018You are now in charge of affairs and must study!\u2019 Meng declined, citing his many military duties. Quan said: \u2018Do I expect you to become an expert in the classics? Just browse widely and learn from history. You say you\u2019re busy\u2014are you busier than I? I read constantly and find it very beneficial.\u2019 So Meng began to study.",
