          textEn: [
            "The rocket lifted off. I tensed every muscle, my whole body contracted like a piece of iron.",
            "The vibration lasted 26 seconds, then gradually eased. Freed from extreme distress, all discomfort vanished. I felt an unprecedented lightness and comfort, as if a thousand-pound burden had been lifted\u2014like being reborn.",
            "I gazed down at our capital Beijing. In daylight it was a patch of gray-white along the Yanshan mountain range; at night it glowed faintly red\u2014there were my comrades and family.",
            "At that moment, someone in mission control shouted: \u2018Look, he blinked! Liwei is alive!\u2019 Everyone burst into applause and cheers."
          ],
